snippet.title: Pinball Heroes: Wipeout HD - 4x Multiplier (Beefiest)
snippet.description: This video demonstrates how to get a 4x multiplier on the Wipeout HD table for Pinball Heroes.  Notice that I purposely light up 3 letters in FURY before hitting the upgrade lock which makes the next upgrade easier.
